            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Cory, what's wrong? Thinking about something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yes..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "...Oh, I know. You go outside the town quite often, right...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Oh, yes I do. I go outside at times. Why are you asking?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I want to know what it's like outside of Kirchen Bell..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "What it's like outside... There's forests, and mountains, and rivers..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Is there anything else?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Anything else? U-ummm... There's monsters?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "There really are...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, there are. At night, even more fierce ones come out, so it's dangerous."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Night time is dangerous? Hm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Is there something you wanted to know?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "...I just wanted to know about the world outside of town."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I don't really know too many details about it either. I wonder if there was more?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Knowing that there are monsters is more than enough. Thank you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "That's really enough? Well, I guess I'm just happy I could help?"
        }
    ]
}